data.description: This 2709 SQFT very spacious home is gorgeous! Sits on 1/4 acre! It features high ceilings, 5 bedrooms, 3 full bath. When you enter the home, you are greeted by an open concept large living area that features lots of windows and stunning ceilings! Large master bedroom with a walk-in closet and a beautiful bathroom with separate oversized shower & tub with jets. This home a large backyard and commercial grade patio slab. The property extends 10 feet beyond the fence. NO HOA!! It is located within 5 minutes walking distance from schools, parks and dining. Owners are willing to include appliances with reasonable offer. All MLS information is deemed accurate and reliable but not guaranteed. Buyer and Buyer's agent to verify any and all information herein, including but not limited to HOA restrictions, HOA Dues, Taxes, MUD, SUD, Special taxing authorities, features, amenities, room count, room measurements, and schools.
